---
// Process.astro
---
<section id="process" class="py-24 relative overflow-hidden">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 relative z-10">
    <div class="text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-20">
      <h3 class="text-primary font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-sm mb-3">How It Works</h3>
      <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black text-foreground mb-6 tracking-tight">From Zero to <span class="text-primary">Ringing Phone</span></h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">A proven four-step process that builds your lead generation system from the ground up &mdash; with no wasted time and no wasted spend.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="relative">
      <!-- Connecting Line Desktop -->
      <div class="hidden lg:block absolute top-[56px] left-[12%] right-[12%] h-0.5 bg-white/10 -z-10"></div>
      
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-12 lg:gap-8">
        
        <!-- Step 1 -->
        <div class="flex flex-col items-center text-center">
          <div class="relative w-28 h-28 rounded-full bg-background border border-slate-300 flex items-center justify-center mb-8 shadow-xl shadow-primary/5 group text-foreground hover:border-primary/50 transition-colors">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="text-primary group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform"><circle cx="11" cy="11" r="8"/><path d="m21 21-4.3-4.3"/></svg>
            <div class="absolute -top-2 -right-2 w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-primary text-white font-black flex items-center justify-center text-sm shadow-lg">1</div>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-foreground mb-3">Audit &amp; Strategy</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">Bob personally reviews your current ads, website, and call handling. Every assumption is tested, every budget dollar accounted for before we touch anything.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Step 2 -->
        <div class="flex flex-col items-center text-center">
          <div class="relative w-28 h-28 rounded-full bg-background border border-slate-300 flex items-center justify-center mb-8 shadow-xl shadow-primary/5 group text-foreground hover:border-primary/50 transition-colors">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="text-primary group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform"><path d="M14.7 6.3a1 1 0 0 0 0 1.4l1.6 1.6a1 1 0 0 0 1.4 0l3.77-3.77a6 6 0 0 1-7.94 7.94l-6.91 6.91a2.12 2.12 0 0 1-3-3l6.91-6.91a6 6 0 0 1 7.94-7.94l-3.76 3.76z"/></svg>
            <div class="absolute -top-2 -right-2 w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-primary text-white font-black flex items-center justify-center text-sm shadow-lg">2</div>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-foreground mb-3">Build the System</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">We set up your PPC campaigns, landing pages, LeadTable&trade; call tracking, and Airtable CRM &mdash; a complete lead generation stack built around your trade and service area.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Step 3 -->
        <div class="flex flex-col items-center text-center">
          <div class="relative w-28 h-28 rounded-full bg-background border border-slate-300 flex items-center justify-center mb-8 shadow-xl shadow-primary/5 group text-foreground hover:border-primary/50 transition-colors">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="text-primary group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform"><path d="M4.5 16.5c-1.5 1.26-2 5-2 5s3.74-.5 5-2c.71-.84.7-2.13-.09-2.91a2.18 2.18 0 0 0-2.91-.09z"/><path d="m12 15-3-3a22 22 0 0 1 2-3.95A12.88 12.88 0 0 1 22 2c0 2.72-.78 7.5-6 11a22.35 22.35 0 0 1-4 2z"/><path d="M9 12H4s.55-3.03 2-4c1.62-1.08 5 0 5 0"/><path d="M12 15v5s3.03-.55 4-2c1.08-1.62 0-5 0-5"/></svg>
            <div class="absolute -top-2 -right-2 w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-primary text-white font-black flex items-center justify-center text-sm shadow-lg">3</div>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-foreground mb-3">Launch &amp; Capture</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">Campaigns go live with manual bidding controls in place. This is Gracie&trade; answers calls 24/7, qualifies leads, and logs every inquiry automatically &mdash; so nothing gets missed.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Step 4 -->
        <div class="flex flex-col items-center text-center">
          <div class="relative w-28 h-28 rounded-full bg-background border border-slate-300 flex items-center justify-center mb-8 shadow-xl shadow-primary/5 group text-foreground hover:border-primary/50 transition-colors">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="text-primary group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform"><path d="M22 16.92v3a2 2 0 0 1-2.18 2 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-8.63-3.07 19.5 19.5 0 0 1-6-6 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-3.07-8.67A2 2 0 0 1 4.11 2h3a2 2 0 0 1 2 1.72 12.84 12.84 0 0 0 .7 2.81 2 2 0 0 1-.45 2.11L8.09 9.91a16 16 0 0 0 6 6l1.27-1.27a2 2 0 0 1 2.11-.45 12.84 12.84 0 0 0 2.81.7A2 2 0 0 1 22 16.92z"/><path d="M14.05 2a9 9 0 0 1 8 7.94"/><path d="M14.05 6A5 5 0 0 1 18 10"/></svg>
            <div class="absolute -top-2 -right-2 w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-primary text-white font-black flex items-center justify-center text-sm shadow-lg">4</div>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-foreground mb-3">Optimize for Booked Jobs</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">We review your calls, cost per lead, and booked job rate weekly. If calls aren't converting to revenue, we find the gap and fix it &mdash; fast.</p>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
